description:
An exciting parking simulator in which you need to show your skills of dexterity and attentiveness!

The rules of the game are simple - you need to move the cars so that each of them can leave the parking lot without obstacles. Sound simple? No matter how! Challenge your brain and try to solve this challenging puzzle in a tight parking lot full of other cars. Remember that, just like in real life, the parking lot is full of obstacles in the form of hydrants, concrete barriers and other cars.

Think carefully before moving any car, because there are a couple of steps from the right decision to the point of no return. Improve your logic skills, improve your critical thinking and learn how to find a way out of the most difficult situations!

Game Features:
• Excellent workout for the mind and logic;
• Lots of levels with different difficulty;
• Addictive gameplay for all ages;
• Management with the Joy-Con™️ controllers;
• Relaxing musical accompaniment;
